msgctxt "an3.129:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.129:0.2"
msgid "13. Kusināravagga "
msgstr "13. Kusināra "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.129:0.3"
msgid "129. Paṭhamaanuruddhasutta "
msgstr "129. With Anuruddha (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.129:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā anuruddho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā anuruddho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Anuruddha went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.129:1.2"
msgid "“idhāhaṃ, bhante, dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena yebhuyyena passāmi mātugāmaṃ kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjamānaṃ. "
msgstr "“Sometimes, sir, with my clairvoyance that’s purified and superhuman, I see that females—when their body breaks up, after death—are mostly reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

msgctxt "an3.129:1.3"
msgid "Katihi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti? "
msgstr "How many qualities do females have so that they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.129:2.1"
msgid "“Tīhi kho, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "“When females have three qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

msgctxt "an3.129:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an3.129:2.3"
msgid "Idha, anuruddha, mātugāmo pubbaṇhasamayaṃ maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati, majjhanhikasamayaṃ issāpariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati, sāyanhasamayaṃ kāmarāgapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati. "
msgstr "A female lives at home with a heart full of the stain of stinginess in the morning, jealousy at midday, and sexual desire in the evening. "

msgctxt "an3.129:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, anuruddha, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "When females have these three qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.129:2.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

